{"id":2081,"date":"2022-04-18T19:39:09","date_gmt":"2022-04-18T16:39:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/?p=2081"},"modified":"2022-04-18T19:39:09","modified_gmt":"2022-04-18T16:39:09","slug":"motorsport-game-torque-drift-2-secures-illustrious-development-team","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/motorsport-game-torque-drift-2-secures-illustrious-development-team\/","title":{"rendered":"Motorsport Game &#8216;Torque Drift 2&#8217; Secures Illustrious Development Team"},"content":{"rendered":"<p> <br \/>\n<\/p>\n<div itemprop=\"mainEntityOfPage\">\n<p>Web3 powerhouse <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/animocabrands\">Animoca Brands<\/a> and its subsidiary Grease Monkey Games (GMG) have reinstated its partnership with <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/FormulaDrift\">Formula DRIFT<\/a> in North America and Japan. The partnership\u2019s fruits will come to surface in GMG\u2019s new blockchain motorsport game \u2018Torque Drift 2\u2019.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>GMG and Formula DRIFT had already formed a long-term partnership regarding the development of popular Web2 motorsport game\u00a0Torque Drift, however its extension into the production of its sequel will see Formula DRIFT enter the metaverse for the first ever time, as<strong> Torque Drift 2 is set to incorporate collectible and utility-driven<\/strong> \u2018Official Formula DRIFT NFTs,\u2019 as well as engaging virtual experiences that will be integrated into Animoca Brands\u2019 Web3\u00a0REVV Motorsport\u00a0ecosystem.<\/p>\n<p>REVV Motorsport is an ecosystem of racing blockchain games by Animoca Brands powered by REVV, and includes popular titles such as REVV Racing, MotoGP Ignition, Formula E: High Voltage, and now Torque Drift 2. Each game is powered by the REVV token, which serves as the primary currency of utility, purchase, and action for the ecosystem, <strong>to ensure users hold full digital ownership<\/strong> over their assets in the game.<\/p>\n<p>The president of Formula DRIFT, Ryan Sage, had this to say on the extended \u00a0partnership: <i>\u201cFormula DRIFT has set the standard for international motorsports series. That\u2019s why we\u2019re really excited to partner with Animoca Brands on Torque Drift 2 for both the gaming side and the new NFT aspect, which opens up some really interesting opportunities for the sport and fans alike\u201d.<\/i><\/p>\n<p>Although a release date for the game is yet to be announced, be sure to catch<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span>the worldwide premier of the\u00a0Torque Drift 2\u00a0reveal trailer, which goes live during a\u00a0<a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.formulad.com\/live\">broadcast<\/a>\u00a0from Formula DRIFT on May 7th.<\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nftplazas\">Like us on Facebook<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nftplazas\/\">Follow us on Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n<p><small><em>*All investment\/financial opinions expressed by NFT Plazas are from the personal research and experience of our site moderators and are intended as educational material only. Individuals are required to fully research any product prior to making any kind of investment.<\/em><\/small><\/p>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http:\/\/schema.org\/Person\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"autho